author: Amai Ta. Yume
text: Thank you JP and EN bros again for the super chat to Rushia. It was very wholesome yet again! Kinda love it how it's funny seeing many sc proposing to Rushia just by "Going with the flow" Kusa! But anyhow, it's the the ending of Redan and his season 5 finale super chat. Kudos to him. Rushia with the ARK stream is my first time seeing it live, so watching her doing something was actually fun as it is! I love to see more of Rushia's streaming again. Take care Rushia! I, along the fans, member or not, love you a lot!
